data.description: Remarks: 4 bedroom 3 bath house in the Country Club area! Currently the ONLY house for sale in the country club area of Butte.  Main floor holds the kitchen, dining area, living room and master suite plus two more bedrooms and another full bath.  The basement offers a third full bath, a non-conforming bedroom, a quiet family room,  a large laundry room,  a smaller room that was used as a dark room, pus two large storage rooms that provide lots of options for its new owner (like a fifth bedroom).  The kitchen/ informal dining area opens to the back deck that leads to the large back yard.  Underground sprinklers finish off the outdoor space in this upscale part of town. Some upgrades needed but don't delay looking at this one! Call Jerry Jordan at 406-565-6031, or your real estate professional
